*'''{{link-en|希薇·聖克勞|Silver St. Cloud}}'''（{{lang|en|Silver St. Cloud}}；{{link-en|娜塔莉·艾琳·林德|Natalie Alyn Lind}}飾<ref name="SilverCast">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/07/17/gotham-natalie-alyn-lind-silver-st-cloud|title=The Goldbergs' star joins Gotham as Silver St. Cloud|author=Samantha Highfill|work=ew.com|accessdate=2015-12-18|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121232938/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/07/17/gotham-natalie-alyn-lind-silver-st-cloud|dead-url=no}}</ref>）
